hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以一早book 定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我食咗兩日<br />\n個人評價：<br />\n頭一日食咗個貴餐，大約6，7千yen左右<br />\n真係好正，入口即溶，真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二日就食平嘢，2千幾yen左右啦<br />\n雖然冇第一日咁正，但性價比好高<br />\n筆直有限都可以享受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：非打手"},{"pid":"dbebbba0fb322ad695a8489c68788ecc358866a2","tid":489924,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"有無餐廳可以一個人去食？"},{"pid":"c4449d30862ae99a2a0fa608bcbaf76541b9e6f7","tid":489924,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>流球之牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次去，平日八點半，門口排滿人，有對香港人話六點半已經喺度排緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講全台灣+香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咪真</blockquote><br />\n但係質素好食過神戶牛，食過番唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食lunch<br />\n冇book 好似開11點 <br />\n我11點15分左右渣車去到 <br />\n都仲有位<br />\n大概去到11點半先開始要排隊<br />\n星期二黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於牛既質素真係好高<br />\n唔係食最貴既都有頂級享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d9ce62c029632249425b26ab6ee6b20bdcb350","tid":489924,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>流球之牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次去，平日八點半，門口排滿人，有對香港人話六點半已經喺度排緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor