rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17167ea23b5a82e8b3cd884b54318eff1741c922","tid":489924,"uid":25992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>琉球班waitress<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北谷店，帶位果個正到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出面有一個大露天停車場免費"},{"pid":"39307adeff217b81eccdf57819db8f20733f1b2d","tid":489924,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>流球之牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次去，平日八點半，門口排滿人，有對香港人話六點半已經喺度排緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講全台灣+香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咪真</blockquote><br />\n但係質素好食過神戶牛，食過番唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食lunch<br />\n冇book 好似開11點 <br />\n我11點15分左右渣車去到 <br />\n都仲有位<br />\n大概去到11點半先開始要排隊<br />\n星期二黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於牛既質素真係好高<br />\n唔係食最貴既都有頂級享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實琉球之牛我會評價為Lunch 抵食。同價錢相宜啲<br />\n<br />\n如果畀得到&yen;8000個頭，JJ也絕對更好食同物有所值<br />\n<br />\n至少佢雪櫃自己揀牛，保證石垣A5級10度雪花<br />\n仲有大將即場鐵板燒"},{"pid":"1d910025711cfbae8c43b8bfa4a66af42f9b7390","tid":489924,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-1